sequenceDiagram
    participant App as AppMobile
    participant HeartBG as HeartbeatService (BG)
    participant PlaybackSvc as PlaybackLogger
    participant API as AnalyticsController
    participant DB
    loop Mỗi 30 giây
        HeartBG->>API: POST /api/analytics/heartbeat {deviceId, lat, lng, userId?}
        API->>DB: UPSERT UserHeartbeat SET LastSeen=now
        API-->>HeartBG: 204
    end
    Note over App: Người dùng nghe thuyết minh 1 POI
    App->>PlaybackSvc: OnAudioStart(poiId, audioId, lang)
    PlaybackSvc->>PlaybackSvc: Record t0
    App->>PlaybackSvc: OnAudioComplete(duration)
    PlaybackSvc->>API: POST /api/analytics/playback {poiId, audioId, lang, duration, deviceId, userId?}
    API->>DB: INSERT PlaybackLog
    DB-->>API: ok
    API-->>PlaybackSvc: 201
